snippet.title: Doki Doki Ace Attorney (Full Playthrough)
snippet.description:
Checking out another mod I downloaded ages ago. This time around, it's a game that pays tribute to the Ace Attorney games in which we have a case to solve to prove Sayori's innocence.

Songs

Doja Cat ~ Say So
Ellie Goulding ~ Love me like you do
Ariana Grande ~ Into you

Additional sources

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z7zgPPBjzBY
Bionicle 2: Legends of Metru Nui
Don't Do It girl
Love Live! Sunshine!!
DDLC Green Passion
Doki Doki Amor Fati
